# OpenSpec Rule Loader

This project operates under the Spec-Driven Development (SDD) framework. 
For any coding, refactoring, or analysis task, you MUST strictly adhere to the rules and standards defined in the following locations:

1. **Agent Configuration**: @ai-specs/.cursor/rules/use-base-rules.cmd
2. **Engineering Standards**: @ai-specs/specs/base-standards.mdc

### Core Directive
Do not ignore these files. They constitute your "Single Source of Truth" for the technology stack, TDD processes, naming conventions, and architectural patterns. Always validate your output against these specifications before finalizing any changes.